--------Inline Style: Writing style inline on each element.

eg,.. <h1 style="color:red">Hi' lets learn CSS</h1>

------Using style tag: 
                       <style>
                            h1{

                                color: blue
                            }
                        </style>

--------External styleSheet: 
                                
step link css file with html 

<link rel="styleSheet" href="css file name"/>
